@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

package "Hermes System" {
    [hermes-agent] as Agent <<Core Service>>
    [hermes-mcp] as MCP <<Sidecar>>
    [hermes-dashboard] as Dashboard <<Sidecar>>
}

package "Infrastructure Gateway" {
    [dockerproxy] as Proxy <<Security Gateway>>
}

package "LLM Orchestration" {
    [bifrost] as Bifrost <<Load Balancer / Gateway>>
}

package "LLM Cluster" {
    component "Ollama Node 1" as Ollama1
    component "Ollama Node 2" as Ollama2
    component "Ollama Node N" as OllamaN
}

' Relationships
Agent --> MCP : local communication
Agent --> Dashboard : local communication
Agent --> Proxy : Docker API requests
Proxy --> [Docker Socket] : Filtered access

Agent --> Bifrost : LLM Requests
Bifrost --> Ollama1
Bifrost --> Ollama2
Bifrost --> OllamaN

note right of Proxy : Prevents full access\nto docker socket
note top of Bifrost : Load balances requests\nto Ollama farm

@enduml
